{"tid":1513213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急法] 屌佢老母, 一陣去銀行拎錢","createTime":"2019-08-28T08:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T10:23:26.000Z","uid":218313,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f5f13b0dbfcbec95eef18265e7b818ca82128944","tid":1513213,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆, 攬炒還攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淋病家下吹到風要立緊急法, 最大鑊係沒收財產同禁止財產轉移<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n緊急法基本上係<span style=\"color: orange;\">法力無邊</span>, 仲勁撚過咩送中23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時難保有百尻幾個藉口去共你產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家個港共政府, 有乜做唔出<br />\n<br />\n同埋, 傳聞攪送中條例既誘因, 係因為中共已經無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想殺左香港呢隻金雞, 去搵返逃稅/貪官收係香港既財產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時一個散彈打過黎, 都唔知會唔會共埋其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARpj3Ne.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARpj3Ne.png&h=06ed2842&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb34660695cd3fb5e5bef5783765c46a03076809","tid":1513213,"uid":168703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0Ypvtp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0Ypvtp.jpg&h=9c33fbd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7962da45fa97f4a61f7c92defa3d7bfea4f2d72e","tid":1513213,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:39:08.000Z","msg":"G7 峰會其實已經比左手靚牌我地，唔跟只有輸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1513002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://